{'dateCreated': <DateTime '20200217T23:04:00' at 0x1a4f2575a48>, 'description': '![](https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1446249/202002/1446249-20200217224506921-95091132.png)\n![](https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1446249/202002/1446249-20200217224632590-1295813597.png)\n![](https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1446249/202002/1446249-20200217225258261-1795723384.png)\n\n```c++\n#include <opencv2/opencv.hpp>\n#include <iostream>\n\nusing namespace cv;\nusing namespace std;\n\n\nint main(int argc, char** argv)\n{\n    Mat src = imread("f:/images/shuang001.jpg");\n\n    Mat gray, binary;\n    cvtColor(src, gray, COLOR_BGR2GRAY);\n    threshold(gray, binary, 0, 255, THRESH_BINARY | THRESH_OTSU);\n    imshow("src", src);\n    imshow("binary", binary);\n    Mat dst1, dst2;\n    Mat kernel = getStructuringElement(MORPH_RECT, Size(3, 3), Point(-1, -1));\n    // 腐蚀\n    //erode(binary, binary, kernel);\n    // 可以传入彩色图像\n    erode(src, dst1, kernel);\n    // 膨胀\n    dilate(src, dst2, kernel);\n\n    imshow("erode", dst1);\n    imshow("dilate", dst2);\n\n    waitKey(0);\n    destroyAllWindows();\n\n    return 0;\n}\n```', 'title': 'opencv：形态学操作-腐蚀与膨胀', 'categories': ['[随笔分类]OpenCV'], 'enclosure': {'length': 0}, 'link': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12324272.html', 'permalink': 'https://www.cnblogs.com/wbyixx/p/12324272.html', 'postid': '12324272', 'source': {}, 'userid': '-2'}